It should be added that the existing gold-backed contracts will not change, the restriction only applies to new contracts, which is to be another incentive to participate in the programme.
"This is the first time in American history that a legal limitation on the remuneration of CEOs will be in place", commented House Financial Services Committee Chairman Barney Frank, a Democrat.
